<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0c96234d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s130aa–5"><num value="130aa–5">§ 130aa–5.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated $2,000,000 for the purposes authorized under <ref href="/us/usc/t20/s130aa–1">section 130aa–1 of this title</ref>. Funds appropriated under this section shall remain available until expended.</p>
